<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.5">
<l>kaṇṇi yeṉatuyir kātal kaṉakac cōti muṭimutalā</l>
<l>eṇṇil palka laṉkaḷu mēlu māṭai yumaḵtē</l>
<l>naṇṇi mūvu lakunaviṟṟuṅ kīrtti yumaḵtē</l>
<l>kaṇṇa ṉempi rāṉemmāṉ kāla cakkarat tāṉukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My life-breath is the chaplet, and [my] love is the countless many ornaments</l>
<l>beginning with the golden lustruous crown, and it is the suitable cloth</l>
<l>and it is the fame that is lauded unitedly by the three worlds</l>
<l>– for the one with the time discus, our father, our lord, Kṛṣṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
